import React, {useState} from "react"; import { Form } from "react-bootstrap"; export default function EventForm(props) { const [title, setTitle]=useState return (
Title setTitle(e.target.value)} /> Description setDescription(e.target.value)} /> Start Time setSetStartTime(e.target.value)} /> Enter start time End Time setendStartTime(e.target.value)} /> Enter end time Max Group Size setMaxGroupSize(e.target.value)} />
); }
